<expan>Schrot<ex>en</ex></expan> czu Schroͣczperg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>, uns hat fürgelegt Jacob Topler,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> burger, wie daz im Eytell Goltstein
                        von des Chunczen Ewterleins, ewrs <expan>eygenman<ex>n</ex>s</expan>, wegen
                        entsagt hab, damit er doch nihts cze schicken hab.
                            <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir mit dem
                                <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>eyge<ex>n</ex>man<ex>n</ex></expan> schicken und bestellen wöllet,
                        daz er sölch <add>entsagen</add> und feintschaft, als der
                                <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> Goltstein <add>von
                                    <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Ewterl<ex>eins</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan></add> gen dem
                            <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> hat, abtrage; und het
                            <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> der <expan>egena<ex>nte</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> eygenman oder süst
                            <expan>yeman<ex>n</ex></expan> von <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan> wegen
                        czu <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> icht <expan>czu sprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan>,
                                <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir im oder <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>scheinbot<ex>en</ex></expan> mit <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt etc. ut in
                            <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan>. Und tut darynne, als wir euch des wol
                                <expan>getr<ex>awen</ex></expan>. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        etc. Und lat uns des <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>freuntl<ex>ich,</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan> bey <expan>dise<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>bote<ex>n</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
